allowance(address,address).details: Returns amount of tokens allowed to be transfered for approved address from balance of owner

approve(address,uint256).details: Allow _operator to withdraw from your account, multiple times,  up to the _amount. If this function is called again it overwrites  the current allowance with _value.

params._operator: - Address that allowed to withdraw from FT owner balance

balanceOf(address).details: Returns fungible token balance of specific address

decreaseAllowance(address,uint256).details: Decrease amount of tokens allowed to be transfered for approved address from balance of owner

params._substractedAmount: - Amount to be substracted from approved address allowance balance

increaseAllowance(address,uint256).details: Increase amount of tokens allowed to be transfered for approved  address from balance of owner

params._addedAmount: - Amount to be added to approved address allowance balance

totalSupply().details: Returns all supply of tokens that was initially created

transfer(address,uint256).details: Transfer specified amount of tokens from token holder to receipient, could throw in case function caller has not enough tokens

params._amount: - Amount of FT's to be transfered

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).details: Transfer specified amount of tokens from token holder to receipient, function caller address is approved address

params._amount: - Amount of FT's to be transfered
params._from: - Holder of FT's to transfer from
params._to: - New holder of FT's to transfer to

transferFrom(address,address,uint256).notice: Allowance balance will be decreased with _amount
